PrecisAppointment of DANIEL J. MARION, of Rae Edzo, Northwest Territories, to hold the office of Commissioner of the Northwest Territories, during pleasure for a term of one year, and to continue to serve concurrently as Deputy Commissioner of the Northwest Territories until such time as he is sworn-in as Commissioner, effective April 1, 1999.
